  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this signal seeking study is to determine whether treatment with BKM120
      demonstrates sufficient efficacy in select pathway-activated solid tumors and/or hematologic
      malignancies to warrant further study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
